The 547cc OHV Rover engine provides plenty of power to get the job done and comes with a 5-year warranty along with the unit too for domestic use. Fitted with a hand-operated hydrostatic drive resulting in no gears and no clutch making mowing the lawn a much more enjoyable job to do during spring. Hand-operated blade engagement.
